  "1709050": {
    "name": "Nitro Kid",
    "steam_appid": 1709050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d2dd1d1112a1833001c48f732eadb66b.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d2dd1d1112a1833001c48f732eadb66b.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d2dd1d1112a1833001c48f732eadb66b.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>类rogue卡牌构筑游戏与方格战斗的碰撞</strong><br><br>- 构筑配合紧密的套牌，内含各种能力、移动与技能<br>- 在敌人间穿梭，打出组合技，并将环境化作自己的优势<br>- 依照卡牌升级、改变游戏机制的融注物和特工补丁转变思路<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/06a4bc725b5f754fed7bd6ec5afe00b6.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/06a4bc725b5f754fed7bd6ec5afe00b6.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/06a4bc725b5f754fed7bd6ec5afe00b6.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>原创合成器波音轨</strong><br><br>30余首全新音轨，来自合成器波与暗黑合成器波流派。<br>专为Nitro Kid创作的音轨，来自：<br>- LudoWic (Katana Zero OST)<br>- Tonebox<br>- Jules Reves<br>- Laird Kruger<br><br>原声音轨可以单独购买，或者在Nitro Kid的Turbo Bundle中组合购买。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/c5550aaa0feaa9fc6889d2c5e57e3e95.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/c5550aaa0feaa9fc6889d2c5e57e3e95.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/c5550aaa0feaa9fc6889d2c5e57e3e95.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>复古未来主义的精髓</strong><br><br>游戏中有我们热爱的80年代的一切——赛博朋克，合成器波，以及对经典动作电影的致敬。你能找到我们藏的所有彩蛋吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/12c3b50bfb6d2a39ae018026480e3338.avif?t=1739398923\" width=576 height=215 /></span><br><strong>三名独特的特工</strong><br><br>选择你的特工。每名特工都有独特的套牌、能力和流派。<br><br><strong>L33</strong>——武术大师，战斗行云流水，擅长使用元素攻击。<br>当功夫不足以解决问题时，你可以燃起怒火，将敌人烧成灰烬（<i>物理</i>）。<br><br><strong>J4X</strong>——拥有棋手思维的重型打手。<br>扛住伤害，并用独特的反击能力在敌人回合予以还击。积累连击和压力点数，然后一招制敌！<br><br><strong>K31</strong>——专业刺客，拥有最先进的科技和武器。<br>用两种不同的姿态在近距和远距战斗中切换。每种姿态都有独特的优势和短板。谨慎使用你的弹药！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d8298e1911b63160c313d04c95244d6c.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d8298e1911b63160c313d04c95244d6c.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/d8298e1911b63160c313d04c95244d6c.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>10层安保等级带来真正挑战</strong><br><br>每次你打通整座INFINITY高塔，都会解锁新的安保等级。<br>每个安保等级都将让你面对更艰巨的挑战。你能与<i>造物主</i>一决高下么？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/eb95944393806246b2d9c41cce8307b8.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/eb95944393806246b2d9c41cce8307b8.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/eb95944393806246b2d9c41cce8307b8.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NITRO KID游戏内容</strong><br><br>- 3名可解锁的特工<br>- 250+卡牌<br>- 3个独特的篇章（INFINITY高塔中的关卡）<br>- 安保等级使难度递增<br>- 50+独特敌人<br>- 50+事件<br>- 30+融注物<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/6780d28891aea00bca8d70b7cef81479.poster.avif?t=1739398923\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/6780d28891aea00bca8d70b7cef81479.webm?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/6780d28891aea00bca8d70b7cef81479.mp4?t=1739398923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
